L02596.png\"></li>\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-L30495.png\"></li>\n          <li class=\"text-center\"><img src=\"hanziyan-L30496.png\"></li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11\">\n    <h4><span>愚</span>字的基本解释</h4>\n    <div>\n      <p>愚<br>yú<br>傻，笨：愚人。愚笨。愚蠢。愚鲁。愚氓（愚蠢的人）。愚昧（缺乏知识，文化落后）。愚顽。愚妄。愚不可及。大智若愚（有大智慧的人，不卖弄聪明，表面上好像很愚笨，亦作“大智如愚”）。<br>欺骗，耍：愚弄人。为人所愚。<br>谦辞，用于自称：愚兄。愚见。<br>foolfoolishIstupid<br>笨蠢傻智<br><br></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>愚</span>字的汉语字典释义</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>[①]［yú］<br>［《廣韻》遇俱切，平虞，疑。］<br>(1)愚昧；愚笨。<br>(2)指愚笨的人。<br>(3)蒙蔽；欺骗。<br>(4)戆直。<br>(5)敦厚。<br>(6)自称之谦词。<br>(7)谦称己之所虑。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>愚</span>字的英文翻译</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>◎ <b>愚</b><br>fool, foolish, I, stupid</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>愚</span>字的康熙字典解释</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>【卯集上】【心字部】　愚； 康熙笔画：13； 页码：<a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/kangxi/0395.gif\" target=\"_blank\"><span>页395第12</span></a><br>【唐韻】麌俱切【集韻】【韻會】元俱切【正韻】牛俱切，?音虞。戇也，闇也，蒙也，昧也，蠢也，鈍也，愗也，滯也，固也，蔽也，冥也。一曰愚之言寓也，無所爲，若寄寓然。【荀子·修身篇】非是是非之謂愚。　又【山海經】天愚，神名。居苦山東堵山。　又姓。又叶魚侯切，音吽。【華竅自責文】聖恩雨注，哀棄其尤。猥命草對，潤被下愚。　从心从禺。禺，猴屬，獸之愚者。</p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>愚</span>字的源字形</div>\n    <div>\n      <p></p>\n    </div>\n    <div><span>愚</span>字的起名意思</div>\n    <div>\n      <p>：谦辞，用于自称。</p>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_en_transl\">stupid<br>Basic explanation of words<br>stupid<br>yú<br>Stupid, stupid: fool. stupid. silly. Yu Lu. Stupid (stupid person). Ignorance (lack of knowledge, cultural backwardness). Stupid. Foolishness. Stupid. Great wisdom is like foolishness (people with great wisdom do not show off their cleverness, they seem to be stupid on the surface, also known as \"great wisdom as foolishness\").<br>Deceive, play: fool people. To be fooled.<br>Modesty, used to claim: Brother Yu. Humble opinion.<br>foolfoolishIstupid<br>Stupid and stupid<br>stupid<br>Chinese dictionary definition of words<br>[①]［yú］<br>[\"Guangyun\" meets all cuts, pingyu, and suspicion. ]<br>(1) Stupid; stupid.<br>(2) Refers to stupid people.<br>(3) Blind; deceive.<br>(4) Straightforward.<br>(5) Sincere and honest.<br>(6) The self-proclaimed Qian Ci.<br>(7) Modestly claim one's concerns.<br>stupid<br>English translation of words<br>◎ Fool<br>fool, foolish, I, stupid<br>stupid<br>Kangxi dictionary interpretation of words<br>[Mao Ji 1] [Heart Word Department] 　yu; Kangxi Strokes: 13; Page Number: Page 395 No. 12<br>【Tang Yun】Niu Juqie【Jiyun】【Yunhui】Yuan Juqie【Zhengyun】Niu Juqie,? Yinyu. Hu Ye, dark Ye, Meng Ye, ignorant, stupid, blunt, embarrassed, stagnant, solid, obscured, and Ming. The first is that the words of foolishness are also all, nothing is done, and if it is true. 【Xunzi·Self-cultivation】Neither right nor wrong means stupidity.　[Shan Hai Jing] Tian Yu, the name of God. Living in a mountain in Shandong.　Another last name. Ye Yuhou cut again, sound hung. [Huaqiao self-blaming article] Shengenyu notes and abandons Qiyou. The ill-fated grass is right, and the run is under the fool.　From the heart to the Yu. Yu, monkey genus, fool of beasts.<br>stupid<br>Source glyph<br>stupid<br>Name meaning<br>: Qianci, used for self-proclaimed.</div>\n</div>\n<div><a href=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148276356684389.png\" target=\"_blank\"><object data=\"https://images.yw11.com/zixing/zi148276356684389.png\" type=\"image/png\"><img src=\"yw11-zixing-zi148276356684389.png\"></object></a></div>\n<div class=\"two_children__horiz_even\">\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_chinese\">会意字。从心,古文字形体像心脏,表示心智迟钝;从禺,禺本指一种赤目长尾的猿猴,以猴外形似人而智力远逊于人,<br>表示愚者心智低下;禺(ya)兼表声。本义是愚笨。<br>①笨;傻:一笨|~昧「大智若~。2欺骗:为人所~。③<br>用于自称的谦词:~兄|~弟|~见。<br>-蠢 ~钝 ~陋 ~鲁 ~氓 ~蒙 ~弄 ~儒<br>~顽 ~妄 ~拙 ~不可及 ~公移山 一得之~<br>愚<br>уй<br>墨愚愚<br>楷</div>\n  <div id=\"yw11_image_ru_transl\">Зная слово.<br>Congxin, древние символы похожи на сердце, что означает умственную отсталость; Congyu, Yuben относится к красноглазой и длиннохвостой обезьяне, которая выглядит как человек, но намного уступает людям, что указывает на то, что у дурака низкий ум. ; Ю (я) также выражает голос.<br>Первоначальный смысл глуп.<br>«Глупый; глупый: глупый | ~ невежественный» Да Чжиро ~. 2 Обман: чтобы его знали другие ~. ③ Скромные слова, используемые для самопровозглашенных: ~ брат | ~ брат | ~ См.<br>-Глупый ~ тупой ~ уродливый ~ Лу ~ жулик ~ монгольский ~ нонг ~ конфуцианство<br>~ Упрямый ~ высокомерный ~ неуклюжий ~ вне досягаемости ~ Гун Ишань может понять ~<br>глупый<br>уй<br>Мо Юю<br>Кай</div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<div id=\"bkrs_pinyin\">yú</div>\n<div id=\"bkrs_transl\">\n  <div><strong>I</strong><i> прил.</i></div>\n  <div>1) глупый, неразумный; тупой</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">这种思想太愚了 такая идея слишком неразумна</span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">愚而好(<strong>hào</strong>)自用 быть глупым, но самоуверенным и решать по-своему, не считаясь с объективной действительностью</span></div>\n  <div>2) тёмный, невежественный</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">淫愚民 развращать тёмный народ</span></div>\n  <div><strong>II</strong><i> гл.</i></div>\n  <div>дурачить, обманывать</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">愚我黎庶 одурачивать (обманывать) наш простой народ</span></div>\n  <div><strong>III</strong><i> сущ.</i></div>\n  <div>1) дурак, глупец; тупица</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">愚!<i> бран.</i> дурень!</span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">吓愚欺庸 запугивать дураков и обманывать простаков</span></div>\n  <div>2) <span class=\"paragraph\">унич</span>. я; мой</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">愚不识 я не знаю</span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">愚以为 я полагаю, что...</span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">愚妻 моя жена</span></div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">愚父 мой отец</span></div>\n  <div>3) <span class=\"paragraph\">офиц., унич.</span> моё мнение</div>\n  <div><span class=\"example-item\">陈愚 изложить моё скромное мнение</span></div>\n  <div><strong>IV</strong><i> собств.</i></div>\n  <div>Юй (<i>фамилия</i>)</div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<hr><span class=\"text\"><b>Radicals:</b></span>\n<font color=\"#0a9ce6\"><span class=\"hiragana\"><b>禺, 心</b></span> <span class=\"radical_icons\"></span></font>&nbsp;<span class=\"text\">(splinter, heart)</span><br><u><span class=\"tiny\"><b>Meaning Mnemonic</b></span></u><br><span class=\"tiny\">If you give <span class=\"radical-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Radical\">Splinter</span> your <span class=\"radical-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Radical\">heart</span> you'll feel pretty <span class=\"kanji-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Kanji\">foolish</span> afterwards. His heart belongs to the art of ninjutsu!<br><i>You were foolish to give your heart away to Splinter. He didn't want it. Also he's a rat, what's wrong with you?</i></span><br><u><span class=\"tiny\"><b>Reading Mnemonic</b></span></u><br><span class=\"tiny\">Splinter tells you to your face how <span class=\"kanji-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Kanji\">foolish</span> you are and you feel your heart turn to <span class=\"reading-highlight\" rel=\"tooltip\" title=\"Reading\">goo</span> (<span lang=\"ja\">ぐ</span>). Now you can't even give it to someone else. No one wants goo.<br><i>What will you do with your foolish goo heart now?</i></span><br>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.mdbg.net/chinese/dictionary?page=worddict&wdrst=0&wdqtm=0&wdqcham=1&wdqt=\">MDBG</a> | <a href=\"https://bkrs.info/slovo.php?ch=愚\">BKRS</a> | <a href=\"https://dictionary.writtenchinese.com/#sk=愚&svt=pinyin\">WriCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.qianyix.com/words/index.php?q=愚\">Qianyix</a> | <a href=\"https://www.yellowbridge.com/chinese/sentsearch.php?word=愚\">YBridge</a> | <a href=\"http://cca.xingtanlu.cn/?action=page&pid=8&do=search&name=愚\">Collocs</a> | <a href=\"https://characterpop.com/explode/愚\">ChPop</a> | <a href=\"https://visualchinesesearch.com/?query=愚\">SimCh</a> | <a href=\"http://www.hanzicraft.com/character/愚\">Stats</a> | <a href=\"https://www.google.com.au/search?q=愚&tbm=isch\">Google Images</a> | <a href=\"https://namakajiri.net/kanjigen/#愚\">Char lookup site</a></p><br><span class=\"tiny\">Examples: <span class=\"japanese\">愚か (おろ.か)</span></span>\n<div class=\"notes optional small\">冂 (перевёрнутая коробка), 厶 (значок МУ), 心 (сердце), 田 (рисовое поле), 禹 (император Юй)</div>","glyphs":[{"glyph":"禺","pinyins":["ou3","yu2","yu4"]},{"glyph":"心","pinyins":["xin1"]}]}